---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy" lang={lang}>
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-premium max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-8">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-light mb-8">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">1. What Are Cookies</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help the site function properly, remember preferences, and provide analytics to improve your experience.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">2. Cookies We Use</h2>
        <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse my-6">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <th class="text-left py-3 font-semibold text-charcoal">Cookie</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 font-semibold text-charcoal">Purpose</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 font-semibold text-charcoal">Type</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-charcoal-light">
            <tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-3">localStorage (cookie-consent)</td><td>Stores your cookie consent choice</td><td>Necessary</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-3">Google Analytics (_ga)</td><td>Anonymized site usage analytics</td><td>Analytics</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">3. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p>When you first visit our site, you will see a cookie banner. You can choose to "Accept All" or "Necessary Only." You can also manage cookies through your browser settings at any time.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">4. Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about this policy, contact us via WhatsApp at +34 655 729 113.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
